PN,36201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,FThe mother of a woman whose husband
OL,7,Fkilled her pets before murdering her
OL,8,Fis still working to create a national
OL,9,Fanimal abuse register to protect
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse victims.
OL,12,F*This article includes graphic details
OL,13,Fsome may find upsetting*
OL,15,FHolly Bramley, who was 26, was stabbed
OL,16,Fto death and dismembered by her
OL,17,Fabusive husband at their flat in
OL,18,FLincoln in March 2023. Her remains
OL,19,Fwere dumped in a river.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,FHer killer, 28-year-old Nicholas
OL,7,FMetson, had previously tortured and
OL,8,Fkilled her pets.
OL,10,FIn April 2024, Metson was jailed for a
OL,11,Fminimum of 19 years 316 days.
OL,13,FLast year Holly's family called for a
OL,14,Fnational register of animal abusers,
OL,15,Fnamed 'Holly's Law'.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,FThere is a well-documented link
OL,7,Fbetween animal cruelty and violence
OL,8,Ftowards people and some studies
OL,9,Fsuggest that abuse of pets or the
OL,10,Fthreat of it is not uncommon in
OL,11,Fdomestic abuse cases.
OL,13,FDr Gerri Moxon, a clinical
OL,14,Fpsychologist, said: "It's about
OL,15,Fdominance, it's about power, and
OL,16,Fcreating a real threat."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,FIf passed, someone with a history of
OL,7,Fanimal abuse would be added to a
OL,8,Fnational register that can be accessed
OL,9,Fby the police and the Freedom of
OL,10,FInformation Act.
OL,12,FAnnette said: "If somebody has been
OL,13,Fharmful to animals, it is a big red
OL,14,Fflag for domestic abuse.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,F"It could be that somebody's met
OL,7,Fsomeone new and they're a little bit
OL,8,Fworried about their behaviour around
OL,9,Fanimals and they need to know more
OL,10,Fabout them. It could be that their
OL,11,Fname is on the register, in which case
OL,12,Fthey can then make their mind up
OL,13,Fwhether they want to stay with that
OL,14,Fperson or flee, and I would suggest
OL,15,Fthe latter.
OL,17,F"If Holly maybe had been able to see
OL,18,Fthat register before getting too
OL,19,Fdeeply involved with (Metson), she
OL,20,Fmight have thought twice about staying
OL,21,Fin that relationship."
OL,26,@{D@Vpm{D@]pn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,FNow a year on from launching the
OL,7,Fcampaign, Annette said whilst she's
OL,8,F'elated' at the progress being made to
OL,9,Fget Holly's Law through Parliament,
OL,10,Fshe's also finding the whole situation
OL,11,F'draining'.
OL,13,F"It's exhausting sometimes. It can't
OL,14,Fcome quick enough. It is a bit
OL,15,Ffrustrating now that Jess Phillips has
OL,16,Fresigned because I don't know if her
OL,17,Fproposals are going to be carried
OL,18,Fforward by her replacement, Natalie
OL,19,FFleet.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,F"With every day that goes by, I think
OL,7,Fof somebody else that is going through
OL,8,Fwhat Holly went through and how it
OL,9,Fcould potentially end."
OL,11,FAnnette has a meeting in Westminster
OL,12,Fnext week which she hopes will update
OL,13,Fher on the campaign.
OL,15,F"It is slightly frustrating not
OL,16,Fknowing what's happening, not knowing
OL,17,Fstill what the proposals were that
OL,18,FJess Phillips had in mind.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,F"I'm just hoping that once I do find
OL,7,Fout what it is and it is agreeable,
OL,8,Fthen things can move forward quite
OL,9,Fquickly."
OL,11,FAnnette also wants education around
OL,12,Fdomestic abuse to start in schools.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,F"I think the red flags between animal
OL,7,Fcruelty and domestic abuse needs to be
OL,8,Ftaught within the school on the
OL,9,Fnational curriculum because without
OL,10,Fthis knowledge, children grow up -
OL,11,Fthey don't know how to behave
OL,12,Fsometimes, and I think it's very
OL,13,Fimportant that they know that it's not
OL,14,Fright to be cruel to other people,
OL,15,Fit's not right to be cruel to animals,
OL,16,Fand that they learn how to behave in a
OL,17,Frelationship.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,F"My main goal is to save lives. I
OL,7,Fcouldn't save my own daughter, I'd
OL,8,Flike to save somebody else's. If this
OL,9,Fregister does that, which I'm quite
OL,10,Fsure it will, in fact I'm quite sure
OL,11,Fthat the promotion for this register
OL,12,Fwill have saved lives already."
OL,14,FSolicitor Catherine Haworth is one of
OL,15,Fthose working on Holly's Law with
OL,16,FAnnette. She will be at the meeting in
OL,17,FWestminster next week.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,F"There are direct links between
OL,7,Fanimals being used as a tool for
OL,8,Fcoercive control within the home. We
OL,9,Fall know this, but there seems to be a
OL,10,Flack of recognition of this on a more
OL,11,Fnational and wider scale.
OL,13,F"It is important that these changes
OL,14,Fare made because there are lots of
OL,15,Fcases that I have worked on through my
OL,16,Fcareer as a family lawyer, where there
OL,17,Fhave been very extreme levels of abuse
OL,18,Fto animals and those perpetrators have
OL,19,Fgone on to abuse their victims in very
OL,20,Fserious ways.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,F"I think because I see it so often in
OL,7,Fmy work, to me, it's really important
OL,8,Fthat that link is made much more
OL,9,Fwidely and doing that on a legislative
OL,10,Ffooting would be really, really
OL,11,Fpowerful.
OL,13,F"I've had somebody who had their dog
OL,14,Fhung, I've had somebody run over a
OL,15,Flitter of puppies, I've had cats in
OL,16,Fmicrowaves, I've had all sorts.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,F"And it's stuff that like people don't
OL,7,Fwant to think about it because it is
OL,8,Fso shocking, but when I come across it
OL,9,Fso often, to me it's so important that
OL,10,Fwe get this message out there."
OL,12,FA government spokesperson said: "This
OL,13,Fwas a horrific murder, and our
OL,14,Fthoughts remain with Holly Bramley's
OL,15,Ffamily and loved ones.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G13/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780427467
OL,3,CBereaved mother determined to save
OL,4,Cothers through 'Holly's Law'
OL,6,F"We are currently researching the
OL,7,Fconnection between pet abuse and
OL,8,Fdomestic violence, and when it comes
OL,9,Fto tackling violence against women and
OL,10,Fgirls, we will not hesitate to deploy
OL,11,Fthe full power of the state."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G14/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
